This paper is primarily focused on the field of robotics and autonomous driving, which falls under the category of Robotics (cs.RO). The paper also heavily relies on computer vision techniques such as semantic segmentation and convolutional neural networks, which are covered under Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for cognition and reasoning, which falls under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of large datasets and data processing techniques, which are covered under Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Computation and Language (cs.CL).
